data.message: Dang!! I'm in London or I would drop everything and come do this! It's very fun!!
All my spots are full now, but if anyone's interested in meeting us there let me know, I'm currently picking everyone up to go to plymouth skyzone.

message: Hello everyone, Nathan Studanski and I are seeing if anyone is interested in going to sky zone tonight. I believe it's ages 15+ after 8pm and it stays open until 11 pm. I believes rates for jumping times are $9, $13, and $17 dollars for half hour, an hour, and an hour and half respectively, plus a $2 dollar fee for sky socks. Quite honestly, you probably wouldn't need to jump any longer than an hour because it is a pretty strenuous activity, but super fun! I have car that fits 5 including myself, and so far I have 3 spots left. If that closes up unfortunately you will have to find your own way, but I really hope that you'll join me, it's going to be a lot of fun! If you interested just text me at 507-430-1236.
